{
  "stem": "24125.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But some of them were such geniuses that they couldn't help it but hire them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In our Ostrog, we had gymnasium and lyceum, and even Hebrew [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] college.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But mainly we used to go to Lwow, to bigger cities to have higher yet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, he did have.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I believe he had a few years of college.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother did not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The rest of the family?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My oldest sister, she did finish, as I remember, high school and then higher.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had teachers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The teachers came, and there were about three children or four as a group.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He lived in Stadniki, and he taught them higher education.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As far as my brother's concerned, Mother and Father felt that a boy should know more than a girl, I guess, because he did go to some higher, like college, and it was in Russian.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I can't connect it, but it was in Russian.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So here we are.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He finished his college.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As far as going down to my older sister, Gene, she finished college-- gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she did go to a school during the Russian occupation for a teacher.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was pedagogy institute.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So she finished that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then myself, I did go to school, and I did finish two years of college and, again, privately picked up when I came to America, USA.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I did go to business college.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It's Cambridge School of Business on 42nd Street in Manhattan.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I did finish there this college and from then on started to work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But coming back to my brother, he had a Jewish education.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He started in Hebrew school in Ostrog.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Went to-- during the war-- after the war, went to college in higher education in Israel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The same thing happened to my sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
